iiitb:brazils_ministry_for_management_and_innovation_in_public_services_collaborates_with_iiit_bangalore_to_enhance_the_use_of_digital_public_infrastructures_for_digital_transformation_the_initial_project_covers_environment_and_land_management a edu:Lab ;
    rdfs:label "Brazil’s Ministry for Management and Innovation in Public Services collaborates with IIIT-Bangalore to enhance the use of Digital Public Infrastructures for Digital Transformation. The initial project covers Environment and Land Management." ;
    edu:belongsTo iiitb:iiitb ;
    edu:description "Brazil’s Ministry for Management and Innovation in Public Services collaborates with IIIT-Bangalore to enhance the use of Digital Public Infrastructures for Digital Transformation. The initial project covers Environment and Land Management. Bengaluru, March 15, 2025 – Ministry for Management and Innovation in Public Services of Brazil (MGI) and the International Institute of Information Technology, Bangalore (IIIT-B) announce a groundbreaking partnership to potentialize digital transformation’s societal impact. The initiative aims to gradually drive the digital government to be a digital economy enabler leveraging digital public infrastructures (DPIs) and digital public goods (DPGs) principles, knowledge and building blocks. This collaboration is formalized through a Memorandum of Understa" ;
    edu:source "https://www.iiitb.ac.in/media/brazils-ministry-for-management-and-innovation-in-public-services-collaborates-with-iiitbangalore-to-enhance-the-use-of-digital-public-infrastructures-for-digital-transformation-the-initial-project-covers-environment-and-land-management" .

