    rdfs:label "IIIT-B Signs MoU with Continental Automotive Components India and Continental Autonomous Mobility India for Collaborative Engagement" ;
    edu:belongsTo iiitb:iiitb ;
    edu:description "IIIT-B Signs MoU with Continental Automotive Components India and Continental Autonomous Mobility India for Collaborative Engagement BANGALORE, INDIA - July 4, 2023 – The International Institute of Information Technology Bangalore (IIIT-B) and Continental Automotive Components (India) Pvt Ltd have entered into a Memorandum of Understanding (MoU) and a Non-Disclosure Agreement (NDA) to foster collaboration in the field of research and development. Additionally, IIIT-B and Continental Autonomous Mobility India Pvt Ltd have also signed an MoU and NDA to explore joint opportunities in autonomous mobility solutions. The signing ceremony took place at IIIT-B's premises and was attended by distinguished representatives from both institutions. Present from IIIT-B were Prof. Debabrata Das, Director" ;
    edu:source "https://www.iiitb.ac.in/media/iiitb-signs-mou-with-continental-automotive-components-india-and-continental-autonomous-mobility-india-for-collaborative-engagement" .

