iiitb:scads_lab a edu:Lab ;
    rdfs:label "ScaDS Lab" ;
    edu:belongsTo iiitb:iiitb ;
    edu:description "Founded in 2021 by Prof. Vinu E. Venugopal at the International Institute of Information Technology Bangalore (IIITB) , the ScaDS.ai Lab brings together students, researchers, and collaborators to form a vibrant research community dedicated to advancing Big Data , Artificial Intelligence , and related domains. Our vision is to create a distinctive research culture rooted in the Indian context while remaining globally competitive and collaborative. The lab provides a shared identity for researchers, enabling us to work collectively on cutting-edge challenges and to contribute meaningfully to the international AI research landscape. Reasoning in Modern AI Systems – Understanding how large language models reason, and mapping these processes to traditional reasoning algorithms and philosophies" ;
    edu:source "https://www.iiitb.ac.in/labs/scads-lab/scads-lab" .

iiitb:seeds_scalable_early_education_with_digital_scaffolding_cags_iiitb a edu:Lab ;
    rdfs:label "SEEDS : Scalable Early Education with Digital Scaffolding – CAGS-IIITB" ;
    edu:belongsTo iiitb:iiitb ;
    edu:description "SEEDS, Scalable Early Education with Digital Scaffolding, aims to empower the children with visual impairment and teachers in special schools with access to appropriate digital devices—including the introduction of feature phones, smartphones, smart speakers etc —that could open the doors of the digital world to them. Good quality access to early education and introduction to digital technologies empowers these children and prepares them for better opportunities for learning, education and good careers. Apart from children, the programme also aims to familiarise teachers with disabilities with the use of digital technology who often have limited awareness and access to it. Therefore, the programme involves active engagement with teachers and children in such special schools for blind acros" ;
    edu:source "https://cags.iiitb.ac.in/wp/seeds-scalable-early-education-with-digital-scaffolding" .

