    rdfs:label "To Recruit Degree Programmes" ;
    edu:belongsTo iiitb:iiitb ;
    edu:description "Set up in the year 1998, and promoted by the Karnataka Government and the IT Industry, IIIT Bangalore attracts quality students every year from all over India and abroad, to its acclaimed Integrated M.Tech, M.Tech, MSc in Digital Society and Research Programmes. The institute has a distinguished history of producing high quality post-graduate engineers every year. The 3600+ strong alumni occupy key positions in a number of corporations, delivering tremendous value to their organizations. They have been recruited in wide range sectors like BSFI, Product, IT Services, HFTs, research labs and have assumed diversified positions ranging from SDEs, Member of Technical Staff, Technology Analyst, Technology Consultant in all levels of seniority. Students from different technical and cultural backg" ;
    edu:source "https://www.iiitb.ac.in/to-recruit-degree-programmes" .

